elf\">2303-TW</a>)、群益台灣精選高息 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00919:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00919\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00919-TW</a>)、國巨 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2327:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2327\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2327-TW</a>)、康舒 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6282:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6282\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6282-TW</a>)<br/> </p></section></main>",
